This paper proposes a deep learning approach for fair clustering with multiple protected attributes. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
